title: [P3D/FSX] fsfxpackages PMDG 737 Immersion package
description:
this is the manual version for those who had issues with installing it.

1) simply copy the files to their respective folders

2) in the SimObjects>Airplanes folder you will see a file called Aircraft.cfg&panel.cfg just open it and add its contects to each aircraft.cfg file as required.

very easy to install I just tested it out 




I included the rar and the extracted version in this torrent


I have not tested it in fsx, but I dont see why it should not work


cheers
